    <summary>Markup extension for referring to other XAML-defined types.</summary>
    <remarks>
      <format type="text/markdown"><![CDATA[
## Remarks

This can be used both as a compile time `{x:Reference Name}` and run time `{Reference Name}` reference.

## Examples

The following example shows how to use the markup extension to reference another element. 

The `ReferenceExtension` is used in the form `{x:Reference Name}` as shown below.

```xaml
<TimePicker x:Name="picker" />

<Label Text="{Binding Source={x:Reference picker}, Path=Time.TotalSeconds}" />
```

]]></format>
    </remarks>
